code: import axios from"axios";export const putStopSpace=async(currentUserId,stopSpace)=>{const path='/v1/oauth/user/spaceStop/'+currentUserId;const token=localStorage.getItem('token');try{const response=await axios.put(path,stopSpace,{headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json',Accept:'application/json',Authorization:'Bearer '+token}});return response.data;}catch(e){console.error('putStopSpace Error: ',e.message);}};
